author: cutting
msg: Move all developer documentation to the forrest-based site.  Remove translations of developer-oriented content, as English is used by developers.  Now we only translate search pages and an 'about' page, which should make things easier to maintain.

author: ekoneil
msg: Fix a bug in BundleMap.  The JSP 2.0 EL spec mandates that in order for a map lookup to be performed on:
the call bundle.containsKey("fooBundle") must return true.  Apparently, commons-el doesn't call containsKey and thus this works on Tomcat.
Fixing this in NetUI so that we're spec compliant.
This is an empty revision for padding.
